Weed 2: Cannabis Madness (Dr. Sanjay Gupta, CNN)

In a follow-up to his documentary, "Weed", Dr. Sanjay Gupta explores the politics of medical marijuana in the United States. We follow a New Jersey family whose young daughter, Vivian Wilson, suffers from severe epilepsy.
